titles.title: To designate the facility of the United States Postal Service located at 5351 Laplaco Boulevard in Marrero, Louisiana, as the "Lionel R. Collins, Sr. Post Office Building".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform.

bill.summary:
4/30/2008--Introduced.
Designates the facility of the United States Postal Service located at 5351 Laplaco Boulevard in Marrero, Louisiana, as the "Lionel R. Collins, Sr. Post Office Building."
